\v 3 Who may ascend\f + \fr 24.3: \ft Qal, Impf., 3ms, עלה.\f* the mountain of YHWH?
\q2 And who may stand\f + \fr 24.3: \ft Qal, Impf., 3ms, קום.\f* in his holy place?
